The '''Pumpkin''' is a [[Vegetables|vegetable]] [[Crops|crop]] that grows from [[Pumpkin Seeds]] after 13 days.  It is one of three crops which might produce a [[Crops#Giant Crops|giant crop]], along with [[Cauliflower]] and [[Melon]]. After [[Starfruit]], it has the second-highest per unit base price of all the normal crops.

==Stages==
Pumpkin can become a [[Crops#Giant Crops|Giant Crop]].
