==Tailoring==
Pumpkin is used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] with [[Cloth]] in the feed to create a dyeable {{name|Shirt140|link=Tailoring{{!}}Button Down Shirt|class=inline}}. It is an orange dye when used in the spool of the Sewing Machine with a dyeable clothing item in the feed. It can be placed in the orange dye pot at [[Emily]]'s and [[Haley]]'s house for use in [[dyeing]].

==Quests==
*[[Caroline]] requests a pumpkin by mail on the 19th of [[Fall]] in the [[Quests#Carving Pumpkins|"Carving Pumpkins" Quest]].  The reward is {{Price|500}} and 1 [[Friendship]] heart.
*Pumpkin may be randomly requested in [[Fall]] at the [[Quests#Help Wanted Quests|"Help Wanted" board]] outside [[Pierre's General Store]] for a reward of {{Price|960}} and 150 [[Friendship]] points.

